As a professional cleaner assigned to clean an abandoned spaceship, you are required to use a specialized cleaning tool to get rid of the accumulated layers of dust and debris. Explain the tool you would opt for and why it is the most suitable option for this task. Your answer should explicitly describe the tool's nozzle, HEPA filter, and detachable hose for reaching challenging areas. Moreover, your answer should entail the step-by-step process you would use to clean the spaceship. Use the following Latex code to provide your answer:
\textbf{Cleaning Tool:} \underline{\hspace{5cm}}
Provide a detailed explanation, with the relevant reasons from the scenario, to justify your choice.
